-- China property developer Evergrande confident on long-term outlook
-- By Clare Jim
-- Tue Aug 26, 2014 03:41AM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, Aug 26 (Reuters) - Evergrande Real Estate Group Ltd <3333.HK> is confident about the sector's outlook over the next 10-15 years due to urbanisation and the country's mini stimulus policies aimed at boosting growth, the company's chief executive said on Tuesday.

